[{"question":"Where are we left here, do you think?","answer":"When we were listening -- we\u0027re in court this morning and we were listening to the state\u0027s case, you know, we were all thinking, oh, you know, that\u0027s it.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":28,"aSentId":29},{"question":"She has such this multi-facetted kind of career that she was building for herself, but what kind of woman was she?","answer":"Reeva was -- she was exceptional.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":62,"aSentId":63},{"question":"How did you hear that she had died?","answer":"That\u0027s very hard.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":69,"aSentId":70},{"question":"How would you sum up the atmosphere given the appalling circumstances of her death?","answer":"It was terrible.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":93,"aSentId":94},{"question":"When did Reeva tell you that she was dating Oscar Pistorius?","answer":"Well, I saw it in the -- in the news first, and that was about only two months ago.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":100,"aSentId":101},{"question":"How would you describe the family reaction to him?","answer":"I think the family are devastated.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":108,"aSentId":109},{"question":"Any suggestion that it was a volatile relationship or anything about all that?","answer":"No, Piers, you know, we were all in shock that Reeva died the way she did.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":118,"aSentId":119},{"question":"Do you or do the family think that is a possibility?","answer":"You know something, Piers, I -- that is what in my heart I hope and wish is the truth because I would not like to think that my cousin suffered.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":131,"aSentId":132},{"question":"And finally, Kim, how would you like Reeva to be remembered?","answer":"For her sense of humor, for her kindness, her magical presence.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":136,"aSentId":137},{"question":"Where are you with this?","answer":"Well, obviously I don\u0027t know.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":196,"aSentId":197},{"question":"What evidentially have you seen which can be backed up by any apparent fact which actually says he did murder her?","answer":"Well, let me start with the affidavit, and this is like a little inside dirty secret in the legal profession.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":213,"aSentId":214},{"question":"Piers, really?","answer":"Well, I mean let me come back to Alan.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":235,"aSentId":236},{"question":"Vinnie, very quickly, finally, just tell me the one thing that you have heard which you believe points to his guilt as a cold- blooded murder?","answer":"He shot first and asked questions later is his explanation.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":275,"aSentId":276},{"question":"Where were you when you hear the news about what Adam Lanza did at Sandy Hook School?","answer":"Piers, I was at work when I -- I had I heard the -- the, you know -- the ongoing coverage all day long, but I was at work when I found out about Adam Lanza and, sadly, my friend, Nancy, who I knew then, who was no longer with us.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":310,"aSentId":311},{"question":"Was that your impression?","answer":"I just -- you know, I knew she loved her son.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":316,"aSentId":317},{"question":"What kind of woman was Nancy Lanza?","answer":"She was a wonderful friend.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":323,"aSentId":324},{"question":"Why would she feel the need for all that?","answer":"I don\u0027t know that it was that she felt she needed them.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":334,"aSentId":335},{"question":"And what does that tell you, I guess, about the problems with dealing with mental health perhaps in relation to gun violence?","answer":"Well, as far as Nancy goes, she was -- you know, she was trained in how to use a gun and in proper gun safety.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":348,"aSentId":349},{"question":"What was your reaction to what Vice President Biden had to say?","answer":"Well, I was rather shocked that he said such a thing because basically I\u0027ve taught about 7,000 women how to shoot.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":387,"aSentId":388},{"question":"What would your response be to that?","answer":"Well, I agree with him that I think an AR-15 is not something that the normal, average citizen should have.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":393,"aSentId":394},{"question":"When you heard Joe Biden say what he said, what did you think of it?","answer":"Well, as you know, I am a gun owner, and I do own a shotgun.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":398,"aSentId":399},{"question":"This one goes in your bra?","answer":"This goes into your bra.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":413,"aSentId":414},{"question":"Are you content that more and more women buy weapons through this kind of direct marketing that they\u0027re like the next Chanel handbag?","answer":"UIGLEY: No.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":423,"aSentId":424},{"question":"What do you say to people that believe that is the only solution?","answer":"I don\u0027t agree that\u0027s the answer either, Piers.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":457,"aSentId":458},{"question":"Patrick, how has it been dealing with his loss?","answer":"It\u0027s -- it\u0027s a mixed sort of bag of feelings because, you know, the three of us, we\u0027re the best of friends.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":500,"aSentId":501},{"question":"How do you feel when you hear him talking?","answer":"Well, it\u0027s that wonderful bittersweet.","docId":"130220pmt","qSentId":527,"aSentId":528}]